https://doi.org/10.7927/np6p-qe61.Description: The Urban Extent Polygons shows the urban areas represented in the Global Rural-Urban Mapping Project, Version 1 (GRUMPv1) dataset. It includes urban areas and provides an estimate of the urban population.

https://dx.doi.org/10.7927/dv72-s254.Description: The Georeferenced U.S. County-Level Population Projections by Age, Sex, Race, and Hispanic Origin, 2020-2100 dataset provides population projections based on different scenarios related to climate change, socioeconomic development, and other factors. These data may aid in demographic research and policy-making.
